{"tid":647392,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲唔見信用卡，求救","createTime":"2018-04-29T20:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-02T04:00:49.000Z","uid":128196,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"94ffb2befaaf324ecfcde2dfddd2059faacb4294","tid":647392,"uid":128196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"小弟應該今日晏晝去超市買野時跌咗張東亞信用卡，到夜晚返酒店先發覺唔見咗。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩打咗去東亞報失兼停用，如果touch wood中間唔見咗依5個鐘比人盗用並碌咗錢咁佢會唔會照charge我？<br />\n<br />\n一個人第一次獨遊搞到我依家好驚，東亞又話系統更新做唔到D乜，叫我聽朝再打過去，同埋叫我去當地差館報案，但我聽朝一早要走根本趕唔切去警署。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打之前有同樣事情發生？"},{"pid":"35546d5451266639fd32671a10e14d40d6d7018c","tid":647392,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:19:53.000Z","msg":"巴打係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4dcb507aa704ca6efe1953d4bf0e173b919fd1","tid":647392,"uid":128196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35546d5451266639fd32671a10e14d40d6d7018c","tid":647392,"uid":28052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:19:53.000Z","msg":"巴打係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:21:44.000Z","msg":"波蘭，講真去差館實雞同鴨講"},{"pid":"5d810360d252d0e83427239d8b9bcc612f16b37b","tid":647392,"uid":64463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:28:44.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"8aecfcd17b9fd0c933777ea8e85ffe1b659ad798","tid":647392,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:30:22.000Z","msg":"你而家去緊旅行嘅大佬<br />\n就算碌咗你都繼續玩落去㗎啦<br />\n喺度心掛掛影響心情又點<br />\n咁你到底有冇買旅遊保險丫？"},{"pid":"605408cdd9da12659e72c7d5873a27f2c7f7b983","tid":647392,"uid":128196,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8aecfcd17b9fd0c933777ea8e85ffe1b659ad798","tid":647392,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T20:30:22.000Z","msg":"你而家去緊旅行嘅大佬<br />\n就算碌咗你都繼續玩落去㗎啦<br />\n喺度心掛掛影響心情又點<br />\n咁你到底有冇買旅遊保險